{
  "stem": "8212.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my parents knew that there was a coffee house called Cafe Jacobi, where all the Jews met and where you could, for money or jewelry, get somebody who would take you over the border who knew how to do it.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were there about a week, and I remember my parents leaving every morning, trying to make these arrangements.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My sister and I stayed together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We walked a little bit through this very strange German city that seemed to have only like tobacco stores and fish restaurants.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was very strange.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And after about eight days or so, we were told this is it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This is going to be the night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was cold.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was winter.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I remember Mother buying us some outfits like they wear now, like jogging suits, brown jogging suits, and some capes, rain capes, in case it got very cold.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my sister-- we left at night with about 15 other people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We walked somewhere in a wood.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then, we arrived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And whenever there were-- there were those big-- how do you call that?-- scheinwerfer, lights looking.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And whenever a light came, we threw ourselves on the floor, flat, in the mud and whatever.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then the light went again, and we started walking until the next light came.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we arrived somewhere in a house, where people knew that we were coming.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They gave us some coffee and things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we stayed there for a couple of hours until it was like 2:00 or 3:00 in the morning, and we continued walking, walking.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we came to a spot where cars were waiting for us, which took us into Brussels.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember it was raining.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was very dark and wet.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
